                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On January 26, 1950, the Joint Chiefs of Staff transmitted a memorandum to the
                    Secretary of Defense in which they set forth “Military Objectives in Military
                    Aid Programs.” For text, see United States Department of Defense, <hi
                        rend="italic">United States–Vietnam Relations, 1945–1967</hi>, 12 volumes
                    (Washington: Government Printing Office, 1971), Book 8, pages 273-275.</p>
            </div>
